Flow Caml 1.06
--------------

* Fixed bug in typing of let pat = ... in ...
  when pat is a sum pattern.

Flow Caml 1.05
--------------

* Fixed bug in parsing of arrow types

Flow Caml 1.04
--------------

* Fixed bug in typing of or-patterns

Flow Caml 1.03
--------------

* Fixed minor incompatibilities with Objective Caml release 3.08

Flow Caml 1.01
--------------

* Fixed minor incompatibilities with the new Objective Caml release (3.07)



Flow Caml 1.00
--------------

First public release.
